snippet.title: Monster Hunter Wilds: 3rd Trailer | Lala Barina & Scarlet Forest Reveal
snippet.description:
Delve deeper into the Forbidden Lands with our latest Monster Hunter Wilds trailer, fresh from Gamescom Opening Night Live. 
 
🔴 New locale: the Scarlet Forest
🌹New monster: Lala Barina
⚡ Windward Plains Apex Predator: Rey Dau
🙌 New characters!
💪 NPC Support hunters!
🍖 SO TASTY!
➕ more!

Monster Hunter Wilds is coming to PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S, and Steam in 2025!

Explore all the Monster Hunter Wilds reveals from Gamescom Opening Night Live with the PlayStation Blog.
🌹 http://bit.ly/MHWildsGCPS
